title: GDG DevFest Belarus 2015 Summary
brief: GDG DevFest Belarus 2015 is now over. It was a great success. We are happy to share with you some facts, emotions and, of course, photos from the biggest Google Developers Conference in Belarus!

title: GDG DevFest 2016 Announced
brief: Belarus Google Developers Groups are proud to announce the third annual GDG DevFest 2016 which is the biggest Google related event in Belarus carefully crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **25-26th of November** in **Minsk**.

title: Call for Papers Time
brief: GDG DevFest Belarus 2016 announced! The 3th edition of the biggest conference about Google technologies in Belarus will take on **November 25-26** in an beautiful city of Minsk.
